mixin cardPlaceholder()
	div.row.row-cols-1.row-cols-md-2.g-4 
		div.col 
			div.card.tapewinder-border
				img(src="/img/tapewinder_placeholder.png" alt="placeholder" class="card-img-top") 
				div.card-body 
					p(class="card-text white open-sans") Create mixtapes to see them appear on your homepage. 
	